#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Pain Threshold
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000600019C16"
msgid "So much pain. Back pain, neck pain, headaches, carpal tunnel, chest pain... no gym membership can make up for working in this manner."
msgstr ""
"La douleur est omniprésente : maux de dos, torticolis, migraines, syndrome du canal carpien, douleur thoracique... Impossible de soulager les douleurs imposées par un tel rythme de travail."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002F00013630"
msgid "\"Just look at those details. So much effort...\""
msgstr ""
"« Regardez comme c’est détaillé. Que d’énergie déployée... »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Empathy
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000070000036CC"
msgid "Everyone is constantly teetering on the edge of the abyss. An abyss of *production*. These squares look orderly but beneath them is chaos, worry, pain..."
msgstr ""
"Tout le monde est entraîné dans une spirale infernale. La spirale de la *productivité*. Ces cases bien ordonnées peinent à masquer la confusion, l’inquiétude et la détresse ambiantes..."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Encyclopedia
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000600019C04"
msgid "You see primitive oil rigs built into glaciers -- by *boreal dweorg* -- yurts under the snow, great mammoth-like beasts of burden..."
msgstr ""
"Il y a des plates-formes pétrolières primitives sur les glaciers (que les *dweorgs boréals* ont installées), des yourtes ensevelies sous la neige, des bêtes de somme semblables à des mammouths..."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700000260"
msgid "Inspect the notes."
msgstr ""
"Inspecter les notes."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100002F00013635"
msgid "\"Well. This has been educational -- let's move on from the welkins.\""
msgstr ""
"« Eh ben, c’était plutôt instructif. Laissons les welkins de côté. »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700001E59"
msgid "Keep reading -- what happened?"
msgstr ""
"Continuer à lire. Qu’est-il arrivé ?"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200000605"
msgid "The lieutenant can't help but comment: \"An inordinate amount of time has gone into drawing these little welkin creatures...\""
msgstr ""
"Le lieutenant ne peut s’empêcher de faire une remarque : « Ces petites créatures welkins ont fait l’objet d’un soin maladif... »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200000679"
msgid "Step back and look at something else."
msgstr ""
"Reculer et regarder autre chose."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200000612"
msgid "\"Who *are* these creatures? Who drew them? Are they *real*? I have so many questions...\""
msgstr ""
"« Qui *sont* ces créatures ? Qui les a dessinées ? Est-ce qu’elles sont *réelles* ? Plusieurs questions me taraudent... »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700000254"
msgid "Inspect the photos."
msgstr ""
"Inspecter les photos."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700000277"
msgid "[Leave.]"
msgstr ""
"[Partir.]"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000005B0"
msgid "Your flashlight slides over an old green chalkboard covered in scribbles, sketches and schemes like some ancient cave mural."
msgstr ""
"Votre lampe révèle un tableau vert rempli de gribouillages, de dessins et de schémas en tout genre, comme s’il s’agissait d’une peinture murale primitive."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Logic
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200000A32"
msgid "Looks like they didn't make it."
msgstr ""
"On dirait que leur projet n’a pas marché."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200001385"
msgid "Some of the writing has faded with age, but you can still make out sections here and there; photos and drawings have been pinned to the board."
msgstr ""
"L’écriture a subi les affres du temps, mais vous parvenez tout de même à déchiffrer certains passages ; il y a des photos et des dessins épinglés sur le tableau."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Electrochemistry
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000600019C0E"
msgid "Albeit dark and cold, this vision also feels cosy in its own way. Like eggnog, or morphine! A much needed respite from our own world."
msgstr ""
"Malgré le froid et l’obscurité, cette vision a un côté apaisant. Comme du lait de poule ou de la morphine ! Elle offre un contraste saisissant avec notre monde frénétique."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000920000059E"
msgid "These lithe, pointy-eared creatures appear to be different types of *welkins*. You make out autumnal *candle-welkins* casting wax-based magic..."
msgstr ""
"Ces créatures agiles aux oreilles pointues regroupent divers types de *welkins*. Vous distinguez des *welkins de cire* qui diffusent de la magie à base de cire..."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Conceptualization
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000005F3"
msgid "This looks like an *enormous improvement* on the classic Wirrâl setting. Much more *advanced*. Light years ahead."
msgstr ""
"C’est une *amélioration notable* du jeu Wirrâl classique. Une véritable *évolution*. On est à des années-lumière de la version d’origine."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700000266"
msgid "Inspect the drawings."
msgstr ""
"Inspecter les dessins."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Inland Empire
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000005D3"
msgid "Who are all those creatures? Fantasies of a tortured, feverish mind?"
msgstr ""
"Qui sont ces créatures ? La création fantasque d’un esprit torturé en ébullition ?"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Empathy
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000920000063B"
msgid "...and for what? All gone."
msgstr ""
"Et que reste-t-il de cette œuvre ? Rien du tout."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000020DA"
msgid "Examine the welkin -- this is important."
msgstr ""
"Examiner le welkin (c’est important)."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200002107"
msgid "I don't care -- step back."
msgstr ""
"Ça ne m’intéresse pas. (Tourner les talons.)"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700000248"
msgid "This old green chalkboard is covered in scribbles, sketches and schemes like some ancient cave mural."
msgstr ""
"Ce tableau vert est rempli de gribouillages, de dessins et de schémas en tout genre, comme s’il s’agissait d’une peinture murale primitive."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000920000062C"
msgid "\"Mhm... political commentary. That one has a great beard too...\" The lieutenant nods at the welkin's facial hair."
msgstr ""
"« Oui... une critique politique. Pas mal, cette barbe... » Kim a l’air d’admirer la barbe fournie du welkin."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000920000069A"
msgid "Entire oceans have been frozen from shore to shore. There are pictures of settlements on dried up riverbeds, abandoned in a storm. Animal corpses in the dark, carcasses and bones."
msgstr ""
"Les océans sont intégralement gelés. Sur les photos, plusieurs campements vides, installés sur un lit de rivière asséché, sont à la merci de la tempête. Des carcasses d’animaux gisent dans l’obscurité."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570000396B"
msgid "The handwriting is only partly legible, but you can still make out three slogans: 'Call in, tune out!', 'WIRRÂL UNTETHERED', and 'Heat death of the Universe'..."
msgstr ""
"L’écriture est partiellement lisible, mais vous parvenez tout de même à déchiffrer trois slogans : « Connexion, déconnexion ! », « WIRRÂL : LE CATACLYSME » et « Nécrothermie de l’univers... »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Perception (Sight)
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000070000036D2"
msgid "It looks a bit like an academic calendar. Only much more *brutal*."
msgstr ""
"Ça ressemble à un calendrier académique. Mais en plus *brutal*."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Conceptualization
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000920000064B"
msgid "If they put this much effort into making welkin cooler, imagine what they did with the dweorg and the humans?"
msgstr ""
"S’ils ont déployé autant d’efforts pour créer des welkins un peu classes, imagine ce qu’ils ont fait avec les dweorgrs et les humains."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700001E4C"
msgid "This is a monthly calendar from the year '50. Cryptic words like 'sprint', 'daily minime', and 'GPI' span the marker-drawn grid -- the grand scheme of production and money."
msgstr ""
"C’est un calendrier mensuel de l’an 50. La grille affiche des mots cryptiques comme « sprint », « miniré quotidienne » et « GPI ». La machine productiviste tourne à plein régime."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000005C6"
msgid "One of the welkins -- towering among the rest -- appears to be different, however."
msgstr ""
"Toutefois, un welkin imposant se démarque de ses congénères."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Encyclopedia
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100007500002463"
msgid "'Minime' stands for a 'mini-meeting'. It's part of a bigger framework for managing work called R.U.N. Station 41 tried to implement it a few years ago, but failed."
msgstr ""
"« Miniré » signifie « mini-réunion ». Ce mot est employé dans le cadre d’une méthode de gestion de travail appelée R.U.N. » Le poste 41 a essayé en vain de la mettre en œuvre, il y a quelques années."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200000A28"
msgid "\"Looks like they didn't make it.\" The lieutenant looks at the frigid ice field of nothingness."
msgstr ""
"« On dirait que leur projet n’a pas marché. » Le lieutenant observe le paysage désolé."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000020D2"
msgid "*Translucent welkins* with organs shining under their skin, and even aether welkins -- hailing from the vast emptiness of sidereal space."
msgstr ""
"Des *welkins translucides* aux organes scintillants, et des welkins d’éther, originaires du vide intersidéral."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000570000025A"
msgid "Inspect the schedule."
msgstr ""
"Inspecter le planning."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000005CD"
msgid "The photo collage depicts barren, icy landscapes wrapped in perpetual night. You see permafrost and glacial landforms, dead trees groaning under the snow."
msgstr ""
"Le collage de photos représente une terre de glace aride plongée dans une nuit éternelle. Des arbres morts enfouis sous la neige gémissent dans un paysage fait de glace et de permafrost."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Perception (Sight)
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000600019C1E"
msgid "The full text reads: 'Heat death of the Universe is the new black'. Another note says: 'The biggest advancement in role-playing systems since the Thirties'."
msgstr ""
"Le texte complet indique : « La nécrothermie de l’univers redéfinit les codes du genre. » Tu lis sur une autre note : « La plus grande avancée que le jeu de rôle ait connue depuis les années 30. »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700001EC6"
msgid "Your eyes glide over four sections of the imposing green chalkboard..."
msgstr ""
"Vous survolez les quatre rubriques de l’imposant tableau vert..."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700001E67"
msgid "A note in the bottom left corner of the chalkboard says: \"SEE THE PROD. SCHEDULE FILAMENT FOR DETAILS.\""
msgstr ""
"Un mot en bas à gauche indique : « CONSULTER LA MÉMOIRE FILAMENTAIRE DU PLANNING DE PROD. POUR EN SAVOIR PLUS. »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000920000060C"
msgid "\"Why would anyone spend so much time on this?\""
msgstr ""
"« Pourquoi passer autant de temps à les dessiner ? »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Shivers
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000600019C24"
msgid "Outside, a cold wind wraps the building in its bosom. Snowflakes in the wind. An old woman passes what the locals call the Doomed Commercial Area. She tries hard not to look at the bookstore windows. It's *unwise*."
msgstr ""
"Dehors, un vent glacé enveloppe le bâtiment et fait valser une nuée de flocons de neige. Une vieille femme passe devant ce que les gens du coin appellent la zone commerciale maudite. Elle tente désespérément d’éviter les vitrines de la librairie. C’est *déraisonnable*."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100005700001E52"
msgid "As time goes on, the numbers in the boxes grow rarer and rarer. The board becomes an empty snowfield in the final days... Only failure and regret dwell in this region."
msgstr ""
"Plus on avance dans le temps, plus les nombres se font rares. Les derniers jours, le tableau n’est plus qu’un paysage désolé où l’échec et les regrets règnent en maître."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = You
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200000618"
msgid "(Whisper) \"One of them is a welkin supremacist.\""
msgstr ""
"(Chuchotement) « L’un d’eux est un welkin suprémaciste. »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200000633"
msgid "\"This looks like *concept art* for a project. It's not really real.\""
msgstr ""
"« On dirait de l’art conceptuel pour un projet. Ce n’est pas vraiment réel. »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000020CC"
msgid "The huldur, the dweorg, the humans, and even headless men... all of them. Purged. Imagine a world filled *only* with welkin! Green welkin, dread welkin... and the high welkin to rule them all."
msgstr ""
"Les huldurs, les dweorgs, les humains... même les sans-têtes... Tous éliminés. Imaginez un monde peuplé uniquement de welkins : welkins verts, welkins diaboliques... Et le haut welkin règne sur l’ensemble de ses congénères."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Drama
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000005FC"
msgid "You should adopt one of those welkins as your *persona*. No longer a mere man -- but a welkin..."
msgstr ""
"Pourquoi ne pas adopter l’un de ces welkins comme *avatar* ? Tu ne serais plus un simple être humain, mais un welkin..."

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Kim Kitsuragi
#. Conversant = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100009200000624"
msgid "\"Some people really *like* building a world, I think. Even if it's just for a game.\""
msgstr ""
"« Il faut croire que certains aiment créer un univers. Même pour un simple jeu. »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000006AF"
msgid "A pinned postcard reads: 'The heat death scenario -- a desperate fight for geothermal energy engulfs the world as Wirrâl becomes untethered from its sun, drifting through the Universe.'"
msgstr ""
"Sur une carte postale épinglée, il est écrit : « Scénario de la nécrothermie de l’univers : tandis que le monde se déchire autour de l’énergie géothermique, Wirrâl est condamnée à errer dans l’univers après avoir été séparée de son astre solaire. »"

#. Title = DOOMED / MOODBOARD
#. Description = Fortress Accident's whiteboard. Has three sections: game-related concept art, production schedule and Soona's notes.
#. Actor = Project Dread Board
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000092000020E1"
msgid "It's Vaarahamira, a *high welkin* -- his face white and scarred like cracked marble. This is clearly a welkin supremacist. The note says: 'All non-welkin races will be purged.'"
msgstr ""
"C’est Vaarahamira, un *haut welkin*. Son visage blanc est couvert de balafres. Pas de doute, c’est un welkin suprémaciste. Il y a un commentaire : « Les non-welkins seront éliminés. »"
